data.description: 4 stories living in the heart of  Smyrna  offer 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths. Location Location Location  This community is central and walking distance to great restaurants, Silver Comet Trail and West Village shopping! A short drive from I-285, The Battery, airport and all areas of Atlanta! An Atlanta address with Cobb County benefits. This is one of the biggest homes in the neighborhood Full daylight finished basement with a large living area , bedroom full bath, walk in closet and plenty of storage. Newly refinished hardwoods on main welcome you, New carpet throughout the house, finished attic ideal for a teen hideout or a bright and oversized study. The master bedroom offers  a large sitting area, his and hers walk in closets . The master bath has his and hers vanities , large tub, and  separate shower.  Abundance of  storage space Throughout the house , a 2-car garage and inviting entryway finish out the interior space. HOA will take care of the exterior paint, roof replacement and deck maintenance. All units will be receiving NEW DECKS in 2025! This classic gated community amenities are hard to come by, including a Fitness Center, Clubhouse, Pool, Nature Walk, open green spaces with lush landscaping and abundant Visitor Parking spaces.   Please stop by today or call to see this wonderful home
